ecution.scratched\" ref=\"https://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/writing/lod/9\">scratched\u003C/rs>\n                                    \u003Cp>The text is placed on the underside of the foot.\u003C/p>\n                                    \u003Cdamage ana=\"#text_condition.complete\"/>\n                                \u003C/layout>\n                            \u003C/layoutDesc>\n                        \u003C/objectDesc>\n                        \u003ChandDesc>\n                            \u003ChandNote>\n                                \u003C!-- Based on Glyph table: beta15; eta05 for 'e' long open; but omicron04 for 'o' long open; lambda08 (and not the usual lambda05 typical of Chalkis). -->\n                                \u003Clocus from=\"line1\" to=\"line1\">Line 1\u003C/locus>\n                                \u003Cdimensions type=\"letterHeight\">\n                                    \u003Cheight unit=\"mm\"/>\n                                \u003C/dimensions>\n                            \u003C/handNote>\n                        \u003C/handDesc>\n                    \u003C/physDesc>\n                    \u003Chistory>\n                        \u003Corigin>\n                            \u003CorigPlace>\u003Cregion>Sicilia\u003C/region>\n                                \u003CplaceName type=\"ancient\" ref=\"http://pleiades.stoa.org/places/462386\">Naxos\u003C/placeName>\n                                \u003CplaceName type=\"modern\" ref=\"http://sws.geonames.org/6535961/\">Giardini Naxos\u003C/placeName>\n                                \u003Cgeo>37.82226, 15.26749\u003C/geo>\n                            \u003C/origPlace>\n                            \u003CorigDate datingMethod=\"#julian\" evidence=\"lettering\" notBefore-custom=\"-0420\" notAfter-custom=\"-0380\">420—380 BCE (so Arena on letters)\u003C/origDate>\n                        \u003C/origin>\n                        \u003Cprovenance type=\"found\" subtype=\"discovered\">Found in Giardini Naxos, near the eastern end of the wall 1 (near the hill of Larenghi)\u003Cgeo>37.82226, 15.26749\u003C/geo>.\u003C/provenance>\u003C!-- add coordinates: these are the general coordinates for Giardini Naxos -->\n                        \u003Cprovenance type=\"observed\" subtype=\"autopsied\">No Autopsy\u003C/provenance>\n                        \u003Cacquisition>Giardini Naxos, Museo Archeologico di Giardini Naxos\u003C/acquisition>\u003C!-- check this information -->\n                    \u003C/history>\n                \u003C/msDesc>\n            \u003C/sourceDesc>\n        \u003C/fileDesc>\n        \u003CencodingDesc>\n            \u003Cp>Encoded following the latest EpiDoc guidelines\u003C/p>\n            \u003Cxi:include href=\"../alists/ISicily-taxonomies.xml\">\n                \u003Cxi:fallback>\n                    \u003Cp>Taxonomies for ISicily controlled values\u003C/p>\n                \u003C/xi:fallback>\n            \u003C/xi:include>             \n            \u003Cxi:include href=\"../alists/charDecl.xml\">                 \n                \u003Cxi:fallback>                     \n                    \u003Cp>ISicily glyphs authority list\u003C/p>                 \n                \u003C/xi:fallback>             \n            \u003C/xi:include>         \n        \u003C/encodingDesc>\n        \u003CprofileDesc>\n            \u003CcalendarDesc>\n                \u003Ccalendar xml:id=\"julian\">\n                    \u003Cp>Julian Calendar\u003C/p>\n                \u003C/calendar>\n            \u003C/calendarDesc>\n            \u003ClangUsage>\n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"en\">English\u003C/language> \n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"it\">Italian\u003C/language> \n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"grc\">Ancient Greek\u003C/language> \n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"la\">Latin\u003C/language> \n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"he\">Hebrew\u003C/language> \n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"phn\">Phoenician\u003C/language>\n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"xpu\">Punic\u003C/language>\n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"osc\">Oscan\u003C/language> \n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"xly\">Elymian\u003C/language> \n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"scx\">Sikel\u003C/language>  \n                \u003Clanguage ident=\"sxc\">Sikan\u003C/language>  \n            \u003C/langUsage>\n            \u003CtextClass>\n                \u003Ckeywords scheme=\"http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/typeins.html\">\n                    \u003Cterm ana=\"#function.ownership\" ref=\"https://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/typeins/lod/104.html\">ownership\u003C/term>\n                \u003C/keywords>\n            \u003C/textClass>\n        \u003C/profileDesc>\n        \u003CrevisionDesc status=\"draft\">\n            \u003ClistChange>\n                \u003Cchange when=\"2020-10-05\" who=\"#SS\">Simona Stoyanova normalised Unicode\u003C/change>\n                \u003Cchange when=\"2020-10-08\" who=\"#SS\">Simona Stoyanova updated list of languages\u003C/change>\n                \u003Cchange when=\"2021-06-15\" who=\"#VM\">Valentina Mignosa added metadata, text\u003C/change>\n            \u003C/listChange>\n        \u003C/revisionDesc>\n    \u003C/teiHeader>\n    \u003Cfacsimile>\n        \u003Csurface type=\"front\">\n            \u003Cgraphic n=\"screen\" url=\"ISic020594_tiled.tif\" height=\"3680px\" width=\"5520px\">\n                \u003Cdesc>I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\u003C/desc>\n            \u003C/graphic>\n            \u003Cgraphic n=\"print\" url=\"ISic020594.jpg\" height=\"3680px\" width=\"5520px\">\n                \u003Cdesc>I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\u003C/desc>\n            \u003C/graphic>\n         \u003C/surface>\n    \u003C/facsimile>\n    \u003Ctext>\n        \u003Cbody>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"edition\" subtype=\"primary\" xml:space=\"preserve\" xml:lang=\"grc\" resp=\"#VM\">\n                    \u003Cab>\n                        \u003Clb n=\"1\"/>\u003CpersName type=\"attested\">\u003Cname>Τιτταβο̄̀\u003C/name>\u003C/persName> \u003Cg ref=\"#tripunct\">⁝\u003C/g> φίλη\n                    \u003C/ab>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"apparatus\">\n                \u003ClistApp>\n                    \u003Capp>\n                        \u003Cnote>Text after Arena (IGASM 3)\u003C/note>\n                    \u003C/app>\n                \u003C/listApp>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"translation\" xml:lang=\"en\">\n                \u003Cp>To beloved Tittabo.\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"translation\" xml:lang=\"it\" resp=\"#VM\">\n                \u003Cp>A Tittabo amata.\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"commentary\" xml:lang=\"en\" resp=\"#VM\">\n                \u003Cp>According to Dubois the female name Τιτταβώ must be indigenous and should have the same radical as Τιτταλος, \n                    variant of Τιττελος attested in Thessaly. As for the disinence -ώ, and not -ώι as everywhere in the Doric context in Sicily,\n                    it's possible to explain it as a Ionism or an indigenous feature.\u003C/p>\n            \u003C/div>\n            \u003Cdiv type=\"bibliography\">\n                \u003ClistBibl type=\"edition\">\n                    \u003Cbibl type=\"corpus\" n=\"IGASM3\">\n                        \u003Cauthor>Arena\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1994\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>75, pl. XXI.1\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/KK5FQVHF\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000282\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000282\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl>\n                        \u003Cauthor>Lentini\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1982\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>181, fig. 8\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/KF8TPJV2\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001878\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001878\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl type=\"corpus\" n=\"IGDS1\">\n                         \u003Cauthor>Dubois\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1989\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>                            \n                            \u003Cref target=\"http://www.persee.fr/doc/efr_0000-0000_1989_cat_119_1\">1\u003C/ref>\n                        \u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/RWXNUFEX\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000187\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000187\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl>\n                        \u003Cauthor>Guarducci\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1987\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>368, fig. 116\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/MQWK2BNK\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001923\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001923\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl>\n                        \u003Cauthor>Gallavotti\u003C/author>\n                        \u003Cdate>1985\u003C/date>\n                        \u003CcitedRange>35-36\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/ZSMBXJK6\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001971\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001971\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl type=\"bulletin\" n=\"SEG\">\n                        \u003CcitedRange>34.0965\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/F2GG87EQ\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                    \u003Cbibl type=\"bulletin\" n=\"SEG\">\n                        \u003CcitedRange>35.1015\u003C/citedRange>\n                        \u003Cptr target=\"https://www.zotero.org/groups/382445/items/F2GG87EQ\"/>\n                    \u003Cref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000796\u003C/ref>\u003C/bibl>\n                \u003C/listBibl>\n                \u003ClistBibl type=\"discussion\">\n                    \u003Cbibl/>\n                \u003C/listBibl>\n            \u003C/div>\n        \u003C/body>\n    \u003C/text>\n\u003C/TEI>\n"],"uses":{"params":["slug"]}}]}
